lead_paragraph: Courtney Williams made a jumper near the free-throw line with one second to go and finished with 20 points to help No. 20 South Florida beat East Carolina 61-59 on Saturday for the Bulls' first road win of the season.

headline.print_headline: No. 20 South Florida Women Beat East Carolina 61-59
